			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">As a Lvl 50rdm I can tell you I get at least 3 party invites withing the first 30 minutes of logging in. This is mainly due to 2 spells that are rdm only. Lvl 33 - Dispel, and lvl 41- refresh. 
<br />
Dispel is a must for rdm to have, albiet it goes for about 70k on my server. This spell removes effects from a mob like protect, shell, defense boosts, blaze spikes.. ect ect.. 
<br />
Refresh refreshes a party members MP. 3mp/3 seconds 
<br />
Another factor is that rdm has the highest enfeeb skill lvl of any class. I will tell you this - of all the jobs ive tried out, rdm is the most work, keeping refreshes, effeeb effects, dispels, secondary heals. So if you like to be extreamly busy during fights then rdm is for you.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
