			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Xen...
<br />

<br />
Be Patient...
<br />
You will not only be desired at high level, you will be required.
<br />
you will have spells no other class will have and to
<br />
take down the uber mobs they will need to be used.
<br />

<br />
You are one of the TWO heroic classes.
<br />
Beastlord and Red Mage can solo at any level.
<br />
Everyone else has to join a gang and
<br />
jump monsters like a pack of little wussies.
<br />

<br />
Stick with it... YOU are a hero!
<br />

<br />
At 20 get your sub class.. there are several good ones...
<br />
White, Theif and War I have checked out.. they are all three great...
<br />
Curently I am leaning towards Thief for soling and White for grouping.
<br />

<br />
If you miss grouping go with Red/White... you will have extra mana
<br />
and the groups will go OOO OOOO get Xen!!! He can do it ALL.
<br />
(And you can if your loaded down with a pack full of Melon Juice)
<br />

<br />
And get some mana/mnd gear
<br />
I am mnd +7 even playing as a Red/Theif... 
<br />
my spells are never resisted allways hit for predictible results = )
<br />

<br />
Final Note:
<br />
If your going to solo get every edge you can get... A Group Player
<br />
can get by with basic unenhanced scale or chain mail or lower level gear they buy something like a leather ring extra armor... As a soloist EVERY spell will be cast at you... Magic defense is as important as physical armor... When a Sonic Bat jet streams you for 130 because you dont have any "Air Defense" (grin)you are just about done. you
<br />
MUST have gear that gives you  resists. 
<br />

<br />
Remeber
<br />
When solo that your damgage copmes from things like Enthunder and on an excelent fast weapon.  NOT from casting Aero, Blizzard,Water, or Stone. 
<br />

<br />
Remember
<br />
When Grouped you are NOT a white... Cast cure twice rather than Cure 2 once you get more healing for less mana that way.
<br />

<br />
Use the Big Cure only when you cnat keep up with the damage any other way...
<br />

<br />
Dhainspell is USELESS! By the time your in trouble there is NO MANA to use with chainspell. Forget it even exists.
<br />

<br />
BUT!
<br />

<br />
Don't forget food... Boiled Crayfish adds to your defense about 9%
<br />
Don't forget Juice... Its Mana regeneration without resting.
<br />

<br />
Recipe:
<br />
Boiled Crayfish.. Fire Crystal.Rock Salt, Distiled Water,Crayfish</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
