<br />

<br />
Seriously, I was in a group of 5 11-13s hunting liz in the dunes (pretty easy stuff) but no one in the group would SET FOOT IN THE HUNTING GROUND without a whm!  So of course we sat there for 30 minutes looking for one before I left to solo... I don't know if they ever found one, who knows maybe they're still sitting there now?
<br />

<br />
But at least I <span style="font-style: italic">can</span> solo stuff that gives 50-72xp.. the other poor bastards who have to group should really learn that a rdm or two can do what a whm can (unless the mobs are IT) and if you have to take slightly smaller stuff than do it!  It's better than sitting on your ass or spamming the zone all day.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
